    gd.jpeg_ignore_warning
    bool




     Ignore warnings (but not errors) created by libjpeg(-turbo).








  Changelog for gd.jpeg_ignore_warning




     &Version;
     &Description;





     7.1.0

      The default of gd.jpeg_ignore_warning has been changed from 0 to 1.








